Strategy_resp: I pictured in my mind restaraunts I had been to in the past. I looked around in my mind.
I thought about sports I have heard mentioned on ESPN. I also thought about sports I had seen played on TV.
I thought about Youtube animal videos. I also thought about nature documentaries.
I pictured my parents' garage in my mind. I walked through it mentally.
I thought about a dictionary I used to study when I was younger. I imagined I was reading it again.
I thought about heroes whose names started with the letter S. I also thought about the dictionary.
I pictured what I saw during my last trip to a New York hotel in my mind. I also thought of other past trips.
I thought of professions that my friends have. I also thought of professions you commonly see on TV.
I thought about words in the F section of the dictionary. I also thought about movies that feature F words.
